text: Chiapas Fútbol Club formerly known as Club de Fútbol Jaguares de Chiapas is a Mexican football club from Tuxtla Gutiérrez, Chiapas, currently playing in the Liga MX. The team plays their home matches at the Estadio Víctor Manuel Reyna. They are also known as Chiapas Jaguar. ==Honours== * Chiapas Cup: (3) ::2003, 2005, 2007 * Copa Mesoamericana: (1) ::2011 Category:Mexican football clubs Category:Chiapas Category:2002 establishments in North America Category:2000s establishments in Mexico
